      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists and friends just... they don't get it. they say 'it gets better' but there is no 'better' without him. the world just feels like a hollow shell now. it's like i'm just performing these little human tasks—eating, breathing, walking—but there's no point to any of it. it feels like i'm just stuck in a loop that has no reason to continue. it's just exhausting.",
